ccessed during normalization."},{"source_id":"bau_grad_spring_2025_news","title":"spring 2025/2026 application window","url":"https://www.bau.edu.lb/Graduate/News/Graduate-Admission-Application-for-Spring-Semester-2025-2026","source_type":"WEB","accessed_at":"2026-06-29","notes":"discovered_parsed_search_snippet — spring 2025/2026 application window; official BAU HTML source accessed during normalization."},{"source_id":"bau_grad_degree_requirements","title":"credit-hour and thesis/project requirements by faculty","url":"https://www.bau.edu.lb/Graduate/Degrees-Requirement-for-graduation","source_type":"WEB","accessed_at":"2026-06-29","notes":"discovered_parsed_search_snippet — credit-hour and thesis/project requirements by faculty; official BAU HTML source accessed during normalization."},{"source_id":"bau_grad_tuition_pdf","title":"graduate tuition fees","url":"https://www.bau.edu.lb/BAUUpload/BAU-Library/files/Graduate/Graduate-studies-Tuition-Fees.pdf","source_type":"PDF","accessed_at":"2026-06-29","notes":"downloaded_rendered_official_pdf — graduate tuition fees; official BAU PDF source accessed during normalization."},{"source_id":"bau_grad_brochure_outline_pdf","title":"graduate studies brochure outline","url":"https://www.bau.edu.lb/BAUUpload/BAU-Library/files/Graduate/Brochure-Graduate-Studies-Outline.pdf","source_type":"PDF","accessed_at":"2026-06-29","notes":"reachable_official_source — graduate studies brochure outline; official BAU PDF source accessed during normalization."},{"source_id":"bau_grad_brochure_legacy_pdf","title":"graduate studies guide/brochure","url":"https://www.bau.edu.lb/BAUUpload/Library/Files/Uploaded%20Files/Graduate%20Studies/Graduate%20Studies%20Brochure.pdf","source_type":"PDF","accessed_at":"2026-06-29","notes":"reachable_official_source — graduate studies guide/brochure; official BAU PDF source accessed during normalization."},{"source_id":"bau_grad_bylaws_pdf","title":"postgraduate bylaws","url":"https://www.bau.edu.lb/BAUUpload/BAU-Library/files/Graduate/Postgraduate-Bylaws-English.pdf","source_type":"PDF","accessed_at":"2026-06-29","notes":"reachable_official_source — postgraduate bylaws; official BAU PDF source accessed during normalization."},{"source_id":"bau_grad_program_scholarships","title":"program-based scholarships","url":"https://www.bau.edu.lb/Graduate/Program-based-Scholarships","source_type":"WEB","accessed_at":"2026-06-29","notes":"discovered_parsed_search_snippet — program-based scholarships; official BAU HTML source accessed during normalization."},{"source_id":"bau_grad_merit_scholarships","title":"graduate merit scholarships","url":"https://www.bau.edu.lb/Graduate/Graduate-Merit-Scholarships","source_type":"WEB","accessed_at":"2026-06-29","notes":"discovered_parsed_search_snippet — graduate merit scholarships; official BAU HTML source accessed during normalization."},{"source_id":"bau_grad_scholarships_awards","title":"scholarships and awards index","url":"https://www.bau.edu.lb/Graduate/Scholarships-and-Awards","source_type":"WEB","accessed_at":"2026-06-29","notes":"discovered_parsed_search_snippet — scholarships and awards index; official BAU HTML source accessed during normalization."},{"source_id":"bau_grad_human-sciences","title":"Human Sciences graduate programs listing","url":"https://www.bau.edu.lb/Graduate/Human-Sciences/Programs","source_type":"WEB","accessed_at":"2026-06-29","notes":"discovered_parsed_search_snippet — Human Sciences graduate programs listing; official BAU HTML source accessed during normalization."},{"source_id":"bau_grad_law-and-political-science","title":"Law & Political Science graduate programs listing","url":"https://www.bau.edu.lb/Graduate/Law-and-Political-science/Programs","source_type":"WEB","accessed_at":"2026-06-29","notes":"discovered_parsed_search_snippet — Law & Political Science graduate programs listing; official BAU HTML source accessed during normalization."},{"source_id":"bau_grad_business-administration","title":"Business Administration graduate programs listing","url":"https://www.bau.edu.lb/Graduate/Business-Administration/Programs","source_type":"WEB","accessed_at":"2026-06-29","notes":"discovered_parsed_search_snippet — Business Administration graduate programs listing; official BAU HTML source accessed during normalization."},{"source_id":"bau_grad_architecture---design-and-built-environment","title":"Architecture - Design & Built Environment graduate programs listing","url":"https://www.bau.edu.lb/Graduate/Architecture-Design-and-Built-Environment/Programs","source_type":"WEB","accessed_at":"2026-06-29","notes":"discovered_parsed_search_snippet — Architecture - Design & Built Environment graduate programs listing; official BAU HTML source accessed during normalization."},{"source_id":"bau_grad_engineering","title":"Engineering graduate programs listing","url":"https://www.bau.edu.lb/Graduate/Engineering/Programs","source_type":"WEB","accessed_at":"2026-06-29","notes":"discovered_parsed_search_snippet — Engineering graduate programs listing; official BAU HTML source accessed during normalization."},{"source_id":"bau_grad_science","title":"Science graduate programs listing","url":"https://www.bau.edu.lb/Graduate/Science/Programs","source_type":"WEB","accessed_at":"2026-06-29","notes":"discovered_parsed_search_snippet — Science graduate programs listing; official BAU HTML source accessed during normalization."},{"source_id":"bau_grad_pharmacy","title":"Pharmacy graduate programs listing","url":"https://www.bau.edu.lb/Graduate/Pharmacy/Programs","source_type":"WEB","accessed_at":"2026-06-29","notes":"discovered_parsed_search_snippet — Pharmacy graduate programs listing; official BAU HTML source accessed during normalization."},{"source_id":"bau_grad_medicine","title":"Medicine graduate programs listing","url":"https://www.bau.edu.lb/Graduate/Medicine/Programs","source_type":"WEB","accessed_at":"2026-06-29","notes":"discovered_parsed_search_snippet — Medicine graduate programs list